<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc8393c2-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s134"><num value="134">§ 134.</num><heading> Incidental expenses of law library</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The incidental expenses of the law library shall be paid out of the appropriations for the Library of Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc8393c3-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(R.S. § 83.)</sourceCredit>
